## Development Tasks

- Configure Alembic migrations (`flask db init`, `flask db migrate`)
- Implement remaining models and routes per architecture document
- Add unit/integration tests via Pytest
- Set up CI (lint, tests, security scans)

## Security & Compliance Notes

- Secrets must be provided via environment variables or a secret manager; never commit actual secrets.
- All logs should be centralized and scrubbed of unnecessary PII.
- Ensure TLS termination in production and enforce secure cookies for auth flows.

Refer to `docs/compliance.md` and `docs/backend-architecture.md` for detailed requirements and design context.
